channel.title: Hp and Prayer orbs not draining
channel.description: i'm using same clients but 2 different sources, but it seems to diffidently be that the sources are the same there very similar.. can someone help me! I can't understand why the hp and prayer orbs drain on one source and not the other.. I don't understand this?

item.title: Hp and Prayer orbs not draining
item.dc:creator: @tank_nation tank nation
item.description:
@tank_nation wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:2, topic:552614”][quote author=tank nation link=topic=671529.msg4490732#msg4490732 date=1437692799]
i’m using same clients but 2 different sources, but it seems to diffidently be that the sources are the same there very similar… can someone help me! I can’t understand why the hp and prayer orbs drain on one source and not the other… I don’t understand this?
[/quote]
Chances are the IDs the sources are different.
Check your refreshSkill(int i) method in both sources.
Check the IDs of each sendFrame126 method… If some are different, take the ones from the working source and put them in the none-working one.[/quote]

Alrighty! Thank you very much for useful information! Really helps alot.
